posting_body: ['Artesia', '11225 19th Ave SE, Everett, WA, 98208', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 27', 'OR Text', '27', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to chat!', 'See our property details here:', '<URL>', 'Welcome to Artesia', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 700 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Life is busy, and you don’t have time to waste when it comes to having fun.', 'That’s why Artesia by the Lake Apartments in Everett, WA is the perfect place to call home.', 'With spectacular lake views and quick access to Silver Lake Waterfront Park, relaxation and recreation is at your doorstep.', 'Enjoy the indoor pool and spa for year-round relaxation, or head to the beach and bask lakeside on a hot summer day.', 'You’ll never be short of things to do with the onsite fitness center, and picnic area with barbecues just steps away from Artesia by the Lake Apartments in Everett.', 'Large one, two and three bedroom apartments for rent offer all the features you have been waiting for, from fireplaces to in-home washers and dryers.', 'Plus, private patios with extra storage and spacious walk-in closets give you the space you’ve been searching for.', 'Our apartments are near Boeing and Naval Station Everett, and offer easy access to I-5 and also Mill Creek, putting you minutes from work, shopping and recreation.', 'Pet Policy', 'Contact for details', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday, Wednesday, Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Tuesday & Thursday 10:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Photos and/or floor plans shown are representational and may not depict the exact layout or features of the available unit.', "If currently occupied, the individual unit you've selected may not be available to tour.", 'Please contact our leasing team with any questions.', 'i9nu1EuAND5f']
